title: List of Paradou AC seasons
text:
This is a list of the seasons played by <a href="Paradou%20AC">Paradou AC</a> from 1994 when the club first entered a league competition to the most recent seasons. The club's achievements in all major national and international competitions as well as the top scorers are listed. Top scorers in bold were also top scorers of <a href="Algerian%20Ligue%20Professionnelle%201">Ligue 1</a>.
